## ‚úÖ ANSWER KEY

**Basic:**
1.B | 2.B | 3.B | 4.D | 5.C | 6.B | 7.C | 8.C | 9.B | 10.B

**Intermediate:**
11.C | 12.B | 13.A | 14.B | 15.A | 16.C | 17.B | 18.C | 19.B | 20.C

**Advanced:**
21.B | 22.C | 23.C | 24.C | 25.B | 26.B | 27.B | 28.C | 29.B | 30.D

---

## üéØ CCEE QUICK MEMORY POINTS

* **Encryption = Plaintext ‚Üí Ciphertext**
* **File/Folder Encryption = Data at Rest**
* **Windows EFS ‚Üí NTFS only**
* **cipher /e ‚Üí encrypt | /d ‚Üí decrypt**
* **Disk Encryption ‚â† File Encryption**

